name: Forest_Visitor
description:
Click on the mushroom, the tree, or the water at the bottom of the canvas

mushroom room: make the fairy fly up into the sky!

ocean room: the fishies will follow you!

forest room: what can unillama do? Drag the mouse to the right to find out!

If you would like to go back to the home screen click "HOME" 

Thanks for visiting ^.^
